#: templates/admin_audit/console/import_fits.html
msgid ""
"Tick the fits you want — each becomes its own doctrine under the <span "
"class=\"chip\">IMPORTED</span> category. Renaming is optional (blank keeps "
"the saved name); you can edit the name, category and description, or remove "
"a doctrine, afterwards. (EVE only exposes <em>personal</em> fits over ESI, "
"so these come from your own saved fittings.)"
msgstr ""
"Marque os fits que quiser — cada um vira uma doctrine própria na categoria "
"<span class=\"chip\">IMPORTED</span>. Renomear é opcional (em branco mantém "
