#: templates/admin_audit/console/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Every automated notification the app sends, in one place — what fires it,\n"
"    who it's for, and whether it may reach a mass chat channel. Leadership-only reports are kept off corp-wide\n"
"    channels: they reach leadership-cleared channels and the addressed pilots (in-app / EVE-mail) only."
