#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"In&#8209;app alerts need no configuration — they appear in every targeted "
"pilot's Pingboard inbox automatically."
msgstr ""
"Os alertas in&#8209;app não exigem configuração — aparecem automaticamente "
"na caixa de entrada do Pingboard de cada piloto alvo."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid "How to get this value"
msgstr "Como obter este valor"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Discord → <span class=\"text-ink\">Server Settings → Integrations → Webhooks"
" → New Webhook</span>. Pick the target channel, <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">Copy Webhook URL</span>, and paste it above."
msgstr ""
"Discord → <span class=\"text-ink\">Server Settings → Integrations → Webhooks"
" → New Webhook</span>. Escolha o canal alvo, clique em <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">Copy Webhook URL</span> e cole acima."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Easiest: create an <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming Webhook</span> at "
"api.slack.com/apps → your app → <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming "
"Webhooks</span>, and paste the <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">hooks.slack.com/services/…</span> URL. For DMs to pilots, set a bot "
"token (<span class=\"font-mono\">PINGBOARD_SLACK_BOT_TOKEN</span>) in the "
"environment instead and give a channel id."
msgstr ""
"Mais simples: crie um <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming Webhook</span> em "
"api.slack.com/apps → seu app → <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming "
"Webhooks</span> e cole a URL <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">hooks.slack.com/services/…</span>. Para DMs a pilotos, defina em vez "
"disso um token de bot (<span class=\"font-"
"mono\">PINGBOARD_SLACK_BOT_TOKEN</span>) no ambiente e informe um id de "
"canal."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Create a bot with <span class=\"font-mono\">@BotFather</span> → <span "
"class=\"font-mono\">/newbot</span> and copy its token into <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">Telegram bot token</span> above. Add the bot to your "
"group/channel, then read the chat id (e.g. via <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">@RawDataBot</span> or the Bot API <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">getUpdates</span>) and paste it. Everything is stored here — no "
"server access needed."
msgstr ""
"Crie um bot com <span class=\"font-mono\">@BotFather</span> → <span "
"class=\"font-mono\">/newbot</span> e copie o token dele em <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">Token do bot do Telegram</span> acima. Adicione o bot ao "
"seu grupo/canal, então obtenha o chat id (ex.: via <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">@RawDataBot</span> ou o <span class=\"font-mono\">getUpdates</span> "
"da Bot API) e cole-o. Tudo fica armazenado aqui — não é preciso acesso ao "
"servidor."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Pick <span class=\"text-ink\">Meta Cloud API</span> or <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">Twilio</span> and paste that provider's credentials from its console —"
" access/auth token above, ids/numbers in the fields. All stored here, "
"encrypted; no server access needed. Note: outside a 24&#8209;hour "
"user&#8209;initiated window both backends require a pre&#8209;approved "
"message template."
msgstr ""
"Escolha <span class=\"text-ink\">Meta Cloud API</span> ou <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">Twilio</span> e cole as credenciais desse provedor a "
"partir do console dele — access/auth token acima, ids/números nos campos. "
"Tudo fica armazenado aqui, criptografado; não é preciso acesso ao servidor. "
"Observação: fora de uma janela de 24&#8209;horas iniciada pelo usuário, "
"ambos os backends exigem um template de mensagem pré&#8209;aprovado."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Any linked Director character can send. Have them open the ESI scopes page "
"and grant <span class=\"text-ink\">Pingboard mail sender</span>, then select"
" them above."
msgstr ""
"Qualquer personagem Diretor vinculado pode enviar. Peça que ele abra a "
"página de ESI scopes e conceda <span class=\"text-ink\">Pingboard mail "
"sender</span>, depois selecione-o acima."

